<b><a name="mq8">Q: Does Multi-Questing still work?</a></b><br>
<br>
A: Yes. Any quest where the reward is given after multiple items are handed in is multi-questable, with the person handing in the last piece of the quest items gaining the item.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<b><a name="mq9">Q: No, Multi-Questing must be broken, Brother Balatin just ate my Robe of the Lost Circle, and the 2 pipes I was getting multi-quested.</a></b><br>
<br>
A: No, multiquesting is fine. You just had charm break before the final trade in, causing an memwipe of any no-drop items that were handed in. Next time, use a fixed duration charm.<br>
<br>
