<b><a name="mq10">Q: No, I'm <i>sure</i> multiquesting is broken!  I just tried to get some velious armour, and the MQ didn't work!</a></b><br>
<br>
A: Everyone who hands in an item for a multiquest must have the faction necessary to do the quest.  So if someone didn't, the MQ qon't work (except that someone else could hand in the item the person with insufficient faction did, and get the item).<br>
